{"id": "1217746792880541716", "channel_id": "1217746792880541716", "type": 0, "author_id": "1204815505916166226", "author_name": "a2548678153", "author_bot": false, "content": "有算力时灵摆不提供加成，消耗偶数都不行，而且时灵摆回合结束提供的临时力量结算在触手攻击后，那这个有什么意义？", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T08:11:00.064000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1217746793077538868", "filename": "Screenrecording_20240314_160342.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 924598, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217746792880541716/1217746793077538868/Screenrecording_20240314_160342.mp4?ex=6a003d94&is=69feec14&hm=a189cbc91a770280774bf33b94a577fabb9a4205995d7dc0ebd2245f0c31d999&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1217746792880541716", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」时灵摆bug还是伽伦bug还是阿卡纳bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
