{"id": "1217835953599811594", "channel_id": "1217835953599811594", "type": 0, "author_id": "354801097065627649", "author_name": "y2k2064", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問隊伍配置是不是能新增一個複製隊伍，\n有時候只是想要更換其中一個喚醒提測試強度，當換回來時又要大費周章的把命輪密契那些放回去", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T14:05:17.636000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1217835954132353134", "filename": "IMG_5169.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2002669, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217835953599811594/1217835954132353134/IMG_5169.png?ex=6a00909d&is=69ff3f1d&hm=3a63fe53d407b1de7e770c0a2adf17262a9d6ab2df11aed18ebc45cbcc3b0d5d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1217835953599811594", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」是否能新增複製隊伍配置至另一隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1217852399247687711", "channel_id": "1217852399247687711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1184260881010405386", "author_name": "chenyu3141", "author_bot": false, "content": "想了解一下為什麼這次活動的體力消耗不能像之前一樣，消耗60體+倍率的選項呢？\n\n120體的消耗個人感覺有點尷尬，如果在上班、上課或晚上睡前處於100出頭的體力，就要面臨之後體力溢出或者只能先刷普通副本減少體力的抉擇，\n改成之前活動的倍率選擇不行嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T15:10:38.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1217852399247687711", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」限時活動消耗體力問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
